Plataforma Europa is the logistical platform of the textile group Inditex (Zara), located in the industrial polygon PLAZA in Zaragoza, Spain. More than 160,000 mÂ² it is currently capable of distribution to more than 1000 ZARA stores throughout the world, with an annual distribution capacity of more than 50 million articles of clothing. It was inaugurated in April 2003 and as of 2004 has 800 employees.
